\nWIDTH - 36\" standard - custom widths are available\r\nLENGTH - As Needed\r\nLOAD CAPACITY - Per code - 100 lbs. per square foot\r\nSLOPE - Adjustable - as required (1:12 recommended)\r\nFLOOR SURFACE - Slip Resistant grooved aluminum\r\nEDGE PROTECTION - 4\" Curb\r\nHANDRAILS - Double 1.5\" bar – standard height 36\" – 38\"\r\nMeets all code requirements for load specifications.\r\nRamps can be designed in an endless number of layout configurations.\r\nADA compliant at 1:12 slope, under 30\" in rise. Except in CA and MA.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993300;\"><strong>Shipping is included for the lower 48 States.</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<strong>PVI Modular XP Wheelchair Ramps</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993300;\"><strong>SHIPPING TO THE CONTIGUOUS USA INCLUDED IN PRICE</strong></span>\r\n\r\n[button href=\"https://store.disabilitysystems.com/product.asp?itemid=85\"]Add to Cart - Choose Ramp Length[/button]'),(20912,340,'_builder_1_content_group_content','field_646262ee50f8a_field_642452df4b3d7'),(20913,340,'builder_1_content_group',''),(20914,340,'_builder_1_content_group','field_646261c650f88'),(20915,340,'builder_2_layout','Products'),(20916,340,'_builder_2_layout','field_646261a750f87'),(20917,340,'builder_2_content_group_classes',''),(20918,340,'_builder_2_content_group_classes','field_646383b921c1f_field_63c58e1babc15'),(20919,340,'builder_2_content_group_style','padding-top:300px;padding-bottom:100px;border-top:15px solid white;'),(20920,340,'_builder_2_content_group_style','field_646383b921c1f_field_63c58e07abc14'),(20921,340,'builder_2_content_group_id',''),(20922,340,'_builder_2_content_group_id','field_646383b921c1f_field_63c58f5259e75'),(20923,340,'builder_2_content_group_row_classes',''),(20924,340,'_builder_2_content_group_row_classes','field_646383b921c1f_field_63fce04310be4'),(20925,340,'builder_2_content_group_row_style',''),(20926,340,'_builder_2_content_group_row_style','field_646383b921c1f_field_63fce05810be5'),(20927,340,'builder_2_con